name: WR. MAKAN VEGETARIAN - PENATAHAN
address: Jl. Kusumayudha, Penatahan, 80661, Susut, Bangli Regency, Bali 80661, Indonesia
review 1:
Amazing little restaurant!
We were a bit skeptical at first, but don't let the appearance of the little restaurant fool you!
It is simple but overall very good vegetarian food and friendly owners - they speak little English though.
I think there was just one dish available.
It was like mixed rice with lots of really tasty plant based meat and a soup for 30k!
Quite spicy, if you don't like spicy food at all it might be the wrong place.
review 2: Very nice local authentic place, with fresh new flavours. All vegan!! Inspiring.
